{"tid":936211,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來身邊有人過身個感覺係好唔識講","createTime":"2018-12-10T14:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T13:33:27.000Z","uid":213441,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe8614f39d73cd166250a0917ec54fb2db75bda","tid":936211,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"其話說小弟早幾個月前去左配con <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁個視光師望落都係50幾60歲到 唔算好老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 配落都發覺佢幾好人 自問手腳論盡 戴左半個鐘都戴唔到 佢都無屌我  好有耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲送左啲俾我試戴 <br />\n<br />\n到到早排想上佢到買啲野見佢唔到 先知道原來佢已經過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然唔係啲咩大事 但有個識得嘅人過身個心真係唔係幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家要好好珍惜眼前人 就算唔係同你好熟嘅都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea236a8036d830dabb4fdb477c08cbd3dfe3e250","tid":936211,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e620ae86949899807b6c12ea4d8efa24db44f6f","tid":936211,"uid":34163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"係 係個種無力感"},{"pid":"fe1e7c93120ad74abc3a90717ff0554a1076c913","tid":936211,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislik